Android Image Cropper (image crop and rotate)
Before you ask a question, please check the app settings and read the Frequently Asked Questions first. Maybe the solution is there.
Also make sure that you are using the latest app version.
A playlist with that name already exists
This will only remove the selected playlists. The actual files will not be deleted.
This will only remove playlist \"%s\". The actual files will not be deleted.
This will only remove the items from playlist \"%s\". The actual files will not be deleted.
The selected folder contains no audio files
WARNING: This will delete the selected files themselves from the device, all playlists included.
Show album cover on the main screen
You can create a new playlist by selecting the wanted artists, albums or tracks and using Menu -> Add to playlist.
Excluding a folder will prevent the displaying of all audio files within. Files manually added to playlists will not be affected.
You can click on the current or max duration texts near the seekbar, that will move the song either backward, or forward.
